            <div class="title">
                Policy Of His Majesty&#39;s Government
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1938-10-05/debates/f7bd5432-b816-4743-9150-af3d280d1fa3/EuropeanSituation" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
